16
00:03:36,131 --> 00:03:38,087
Ina?

17
00:03:39,012 --> 00:03:41,502
Má ozaj dobrý hlas.

18
00:03:41,502 --> 00:03:43,777
Ale prečo neukáže svoju tvár? Je strašne škaredá alebo čo?

19
00:03:43,777 --> 00:03:47,195
